
Tune Params:
===========

-period      set the topocentric center period (ms)
-bary-period set the barycentric center period (ms)
-accn        set the centre acceleration (m/s/s)
-jerk        set the centre jerk (adot) (m/s/s/s)

-useaccn     search in accn space
-usejerk     search in jerk space

-period-range set the period search range (ms)
-accn-range   set the acceleration search range (m/s/s)
-jerk-range   set the jerk (adot) search range (m/s/s/s)
-dm-range     set the dm search range (cm^-3/pc)
-period-range set the period search step size (ms)
-accn-range   set the acceleration search step size (m/s/s)
-jerk-range   set the jerk (adot) search step size (m/s/s/s)
-dm-range     set the dm search step size (cm^-3/pc)

-harmonic     multiply the period by this value

-nbins        set the number of bins in the output profile
-nsub         set the number of subints to use
-ibands       give comma seperated list of bands to ignore
-isub         give comma seperated list of subints to ignore
-iloudsints   specify rms threashold above which subints are ignored (compared to mean rms)

Untested Options:
-fudge-initial-snr Force set the 'initial snr' to be the folded, but unoptimised snr
-interactive       Use the 'interactive RFI zapper'. Useful, but far from finished.
        
